Package curam.util.client.domain.convert

Contains functionality that allows the conversion of data from the application server into the string format displayed on the web page and parses the string format entered by the user to the type required by the application server.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DomainConverter
    A domain plug-in class that converts data in the form supplied by the application server to and from a string representation used by the web tier.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractConverter
    An abstract class for converters that implements the basic plug-in interface methods.
    BirthdateConverter
    A converter for the THREE_FIELD_DATE domain.
    CodeTableCodeConverter
    A converter for code-table code items.
    CuramTimeConverter
    A converter for the CURAM_TIME domain, a core derivative of the SVR_DATETIME domain.
    DateTimeConverter
    A converter for the SVR_DATETIME domain.
    DynamicTypeConverter
    A converter for string data representing values in any domain.
    FrequencyPatternConverter
    A converter plug-in for frequency patterns.
    InternalIDConverter
    Converter for the INTERNAL_ID domain.
    LocalizedMessageConverter
    Overrides the converter used by SVR_UNBOUNDED_STRING and SVR_STRING to format LOCALIZED_MESSAGE domain values.
    SvrBlobConverter
    A converter for the SVR_BLOB domain.
    SvrBooleanConverter
    A converter for the SVR_BOOLEAN domain.
    SvrCharConverter
    A converter for the SVR_CHAR domain.
    SvrDateConverter
    A converter for the SVR_DATE domain.
    SvrDateTimeConverter
    A converter for the SVR_DATETIME domain.
    SvrDoubleConverter
    A converter for the SVR_DOUBLE domain.
    SvrDoubleOneDecimalPlaceConvertor
    A converter for the RATE_STRING domain.
    SvrFloatConverter
    A converter for the SVR_FLOAT domain.
    SvrInt16BareConverter
    Converter for the SVR_INT16 domain that formats and parses values in a non-locale-specific manner.
    SvrInt16Converter
    A converter for the SVR_INT16 domain.
    SvrInt32BareConverter
    Converter for the SVR_INT32 domain that formats and parses values in a non-locale-specific manner.
    SvrInt32Converter
    A converter for the SVR_INT32 domain.
    SvrInt64BareConverter
    Converter for the SVR_INT64 domain that formats and parses values in a non-locale-specific manner.
    SvrInt64Converter
    A converter for the SVR_INT64 domain.
    SvrInt8BareConverter
    Converter for the SVR_INT8 domain that formats and parses values in a non-locale-specific manner.
    SvrInt8Converter
    A converter for the SVR_INT8 domain.
    SvrMoneyConverter
    A converter for the SVR_MONEY domain.
    SvrStringConverter
    A converter for the SVR_STRING domain and its derivatives.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConversionException
    Exception class for data conversion problems.

Package curam.util.client.domain.convert Description

Contains functionality that allows the conversion of data from the application server into the string format displayed on the web page and parses the string format entered by the user to the type required by the application server.
